ENST 490	Seminar in Environmental Studies	"In this senior seminar, students discuss the relevant literature (from multiple disciplines) and do research on one or more selected environmental issue or issues, chosen by the instructor. Topics differ from year to year. The goal is to achieve an advanced, interdisciplinary understanding of contemporary environmental issues."	ENST	3	ENST 390 or ENST 389 or permission of the ENST director			
